[[File:Mission_to_Goratek_III.png|thumb|right|250px|The Crystal Forests of Goratak III]]
The '''Crystal Forests''' were a part of the landscape of [[Goratak III]]. They were described as "crystalline wilderness" covering the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. The [[Mission to Goratak III]], a battle between [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] and [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] teams, took place in the Crystal Forests.<ref name="WEG">{{WEGCite|story=The Crystal Forest of Goratak|book=Star Wars Miniatures Battles (first edition)|reprint=1}}</ref>

